      <title>LCS问题-动态规划法</title>
      <link href="2020/09/30/LCS%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98-%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E6%B3%95/"/>
      <url>2020/09/30/LCS%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98-%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E6%B3%95/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="LCS最长公共子字符串问题"><a href="#LCS最长公共子字符串问题" class="headerlink" title="LCS最长公共子字符串问题"></a>LCS最长公共子字符串问题</h1><blockquote><p>这是我大一时进组的面试题，基础很薄弱，没接触过算法，希望能对纯萌新有点帮助吧！</p></blockquote><h1 id="确定长度"><a href="#确定长度" class="headerlink" title="确定长度"></a>确定长度</h1><p>对于任意的两个序列：$X[m]={x_1,x_2,x_3,…,x_m}$和$Y[n]={y_1,y_2,y_3,…,y_n}$</p><p>记$c[m][n]$为$X[m]$和$Y[n]$最长公共子序列（LCS）的长度</p><p>$x_m=y_n$就表示$x_m(y_n)$一定在最长公共子序列中，所以：</p><p><strong>$c[m][n]=c[m-1][n-1]+1$</strong></p><p>因为我们已经确定了一个元素，接下来我们只考虑X[m-1]和Y[n-1]中的元素，求c[m-1][n-1]的值。</p><p>如果X(m-1)== Y(n-1)我们就可以根据上面的方法继续寻找。</p><p>如果$X(m-1)！= Y(n-1)$，这说明$X（m-1）$或$Y（n-1）$有一个元素不属于最长公共子序列，那么有：</p><p><strong>$c[m][n]=MAX(c[m-1][n-2],c[m-2][n-1])$</strong></p><p>也就是说我们去除了一个元素，取剩余两序列最长公共子序列长度的最大值（如果去除的是最长公共子序列的元素，长度必然会-1，所以取最大值）。</p><p>根据上述方法，不断的向上寻找我们就会到达c[0][]或c[][0]，即我们到了边界。这种情况就很简单了，空序列与任何序列的公共序列长度只能是0。即</p><p><strong>$c[ ][0]或c[0][ ]=0$</strong></p><p>通过上面的说明，我们已经将所有的情况都解决了。总结起来就是</p><p><strong>$c[i][j]=\begin{cases} 0, i≤0或j≤0\\c[i-1][j-1]+1,i&gt;0,j&gt;0且X_i=Y_j\\ MAX(c[i][j-1],c[i-1][j]),i&gt;0,j&gt;0且X_i≠Y_j\end{cases}$</strong></p><p>可以发现，要得到$c[i][j]$我们就要知道$c[m-1][n-1]，c[m][n-1]，c[m-1][n]，$所以我们可以从最底部开始，逐步得到$c[i][j]$。至此，我们就得到了最长公共子序列的长度。</p><h1 id="确定元素"><a href="#确定元素" class="headerlink" title="确定元素"></a>确定元素</h1><p>通过上面的方法，我们发现在Xi=Yj时这个元素被确定了，所以我们要做个标记：</p><p><strong>$b[i][j]=0$</strong></p><p>这表示，我们要的元素是$x_i(y_j)$。</p><p>接下来，我们要做的不是遍历整个$b[i][j]$，找到所有为0的点，而是通过做标记，告诉程序怎么走才能完整，无重复无遗漏的找出所有我们需要的元素。</p><h2 id="情况1："><a href="#情况1：" class="headerlink" title="情况1："></a>情况1：</h2><p><strong>$Xi=Yj，记b[i][j]=0$</strong></p><p>这时，我们就会发现在$X[i]$和$Y[j-1]$，$X[i-1]$和$Y[j]$寻找没什么意义，因为$Xi=Yj$已经被我们确定了，不如直接在$X[i-1]$和$Y[j-1]$寻找。所以我们要告诉程序$i—，j—$。</p><h2 id="情况2："><a href="#情况2：" class="headerlink" title="情况2："></a>情况2：</h2><p><strong>$c[i][j-1]&gt;c[i-1][j]，记b[i][j]=1$</strong></p><p>这说明在$X[i]$和$Y[j-1]$中有我们要的元素，所以$j—$。</p><h2 id="情况3："><a href="#情况3：" class="headerlink" title="情况3："></a>情况3：</h2><p><strong>$c[i][j-1]≤c[ⅈ-1][j]，记b[i][j]=-1$</strong></p><p>这说明在$X[i-1]和Y[j]$一定中有我们要的元素，所以i—。等于的情况向什么方向寻找都可以，我们将其与小于归为一类。</p><p>至此，我们就可以从$b[m][n]$开始回收我们做的标记，记录对应的序列值就得到了，$X[m]$和$ Y[n]$的最长公共子序列。</p><h1 id="Code"><a href="#Code" class="headerlink" title="Code"></a>Code</h1><p>下面附上我的代码：</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;string.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">MAX</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> x,<span class="keyword">int</span> y,<span class="keyword">int</span> i,<span class="keyword">int</span> j)</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">LCS</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> i,<span class="keyword">int</span> j ,<span class="keyword">int</span> n ,<span class="keyword">char</span> x[],<span class="keyword">char</span> y[])</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> c[<span class="number">255</span>][<span class="number">255</span>];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> b[<span class="number">255</span>][<span class="number">255</span>];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">char</span> flag[<span class="number">255</span>];</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">char</span> X[<span class="number">255</span>],Y[<span class="number">255</span>];</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">int</span> i,j,m,n;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">scanf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;%s&quot;</span>,X);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">scanf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;%s&quot;</span>,Y);</span><br><span class="line">m=<span class="built_in">strlen</span>(X);</span><br><span class="line">n=<span class="built_in">strlen</span>(Y);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> (i = <span class="number">1</span>;i&lt;=m;i++)<span class="comment">//采用循环嵌套的结构从底层开始获取子序列长度</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>(j=<span class="number">1</span>;j&lt;=n;j++)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> (X[i<span class="number">-1</span>]==Y[j<span class="number">-1</span>])</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">c[i][j]=c[i<span class="number">-1</span>][j<span class="number">-1</span>]+<span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">b[i][j]=<span class="number">0</span>;<span class="comment">//b=0代表此时对应的X[i-1]或Y[j-1]为子序列的一个元素</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;<span class="comment">//此时我们应该向左上方回溯</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">c[i][j]=MAX(c[i][j<span class="number">-1</span>],c[i<span class="number">-1</span>][j],i,j);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;length:%d\n&quot;</span>,c[m][n]);</span><br><span class="line">LCS(m,n,c[m][n],X,Y);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">MAX</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> x,<span class="keyword">int</span> y,<span class="keyword">int</span> i,<span class="keyword">int</span> j)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(x&gt;y)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">b[i][j]=<span class="number">-1</span>;<span class="comment">//x&gt;y说明左侧序列长度大于上侧，应向左回溯寻找元素，记为-1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> x;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">else</span> </span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">b[i][j]=<span class="number">1</span>;<span class="comment">//同理，向上回溯，记为1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> y;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">LCS</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> i,<span class="keyword">int</span> j,<span class="keyword">int</span> n,<span class="keyword">char</span> x[],<span class="keyword">char</span> y[])</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">while</span> (i&gt;<span class="number">0</span>&amp;&amp;j&gt;<span class="number">0</span>)<span class="comment">//从底层开始程序根据我们设计的标记记录元素</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(b[i][j]==<span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">flag[n<span class="number">-1</span>]=x[i<span class="number">-1</span>];<span class="comment">//记录当前元素</span></span><br><span class="line">n--;</span><br><span class="line">i--;</span><br><span class="line">j--;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span> (b[i][j]==<span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">i--;<span class="comment">//向上回溯，行数-1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">j--;<span class="comment">//向左回溯，列数-1</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">&quot;result:%s&quot;</span>,flag);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
